        dc:description           "FIG. 4. — A, Petrolisthes hispaniolensis Werding & Miller, 2005, 1 ♂ 3.3 × 3.2 mm, MNHN-IU-2013-7156, st. GM22; B, Petrolisthes jugosus Streets, 1872, 1 ♀ 3.8 × 4.1 mm, MNHN-IU-2013-5292, st. GM07; C, Petrolisthes politus Gray, 1831, 1 ♀ ov. 6.0 × 6.3 mm, MNHN-IU-2013-5076, st. GM07; D, E, Petrolisthes quadratus Benedict, 1901; D, 1 ♀ 4.0 × 4.1 mm, MNHN-IU-2013-5298, st. GM10; E, 1 ♂ 3.5 × 3.5 mm, MNHN-IU-2013-6886 (right cheliped is detached), st. GM10; F, Petrolisthes rosariensis Werding, 1978, 1 ♀ 3.3 × 3.0 mm, MNHN-IU-2013-5427, st. GD20 (preserved specimen); G, Porcellana sayana (Leach, 1820), 1 ♂ 9.9 × 9.1 mm, MNHN- IU-2013-4985, st. GR31; H, Porcellana sigsbeiana A. Milne-Edwards, 1880, 1 ♂ 3.1 × 2.6 mm, MNHN-IU-2013-5218, st. GB17. Magnification is about × 3 for C, G, and × 5 for the others species." ;
